        {
            "title": "威剛3月營收破百億元續創高 Q2合約價至少再漲4成",
            "description": "<div class=\"atoms\"><figure class=\"mb-module-gap\"><div class=\"mx-auto w-fit max-w-full\"><img alt=\"\" class=\"rounded-lg\" height=\"214\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/jEHqsNLTk9I95LLjho3FnQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTcwNTtoPTM5Nw--/https://media.zenfs.com/ko/cnyes_hk_559/945e28812e61094b3e2938a1961d7b86\" width=\"380\"/></div></figure></div>",
